longBusinessSummary: Hyve Group Plc engages in the organization of trade exhibitions, conferences, and related activities. The company serves technology, beauty and healthcare, building and interior, education technology, energy, fashion, food and packaging, manufacturing industrial technology, retail, transport and logistic, travel and tourism, and other sectors. It operates in Asia, central Asia, Eastern and Southern Europe, Russia, the United Kingdom, and internationally. The company was formerly known as ITE Group plc and changed its name to Hyve Group Plc in September 2019. Hyve Group Plc was incorporated in 1985 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
